name: census-block-groups-new-york-state-shapefile-1999
notes: These data are a selection of geographic and cartographic information from the 1998 TIGER/Line files detailing block groups. This dataset includes geographic block groups, tabulation block groups, and block group number record locations. CUGIR, The Cornell University Geospatial Information Repository, using US Department of Commerce, Bureau of the Census data, developed the GIS data set versions of 1998 Census TIGER/Line files for 10 coverages for each of the 62 counties in New York State.
